Japanese stock futures fell after
the Bank of Japan released a policy statement. The yen gained.  Nikkei 225 Stock Average futures traded in  Singapore 
dropped 1.1 percent to 13,400 as of 11:49 a.m. in Tokyo.  To contact the reporter on this story:
